==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''time travel''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#[[Hypothetical]] or [[fictional]] [[travel]] at will to a [[time]] in the [[past]] or the [[future]], typically by means of a machine (a [[time machine]]) or a [[wormhole]].  It is also good to know the risk of time travel, and that your safety may not neccesarily be guaranteed, especially if you are going with someone who has only done this once before. Make sure you take your own weapons, and if successful, you will get paid on your return. Be sure to push it to the limit. 


